# Plan Backup

When a plan from `.cursor/plans/` is fully completed (all todos marked as completed):

1. Copy the plan file to `docs/plans/` using a clean filename derived from the plan name
2. Strip the YAML frontmatter (todo statuses are no longer relevant once completed)
3. Keep only the markdown content as implementation documentation
4. Stage the backup file in the next commit

This ensures implementation decisions and architecture docs are preserved in the repo.
